      <description>&lt;div&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/00d6c8bef96e111284334c160ba2438745a2044d.png?auto=compress,format&amp;h=340&amp;w=1200&amp;s=6f980628fa650ad71e665d191b77fef3"&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/9a40db9434c0c783b104e713d0d68d70d264f3a0.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=crop&amp;h=600&amp;w=1200&amp;s=d0fc61353bb2e3b63a79d7b774252a80"&gt;&lt;h2&gt;Space: The final frontier—of comics&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;Captain the Starship Enterprise from the comfort of your own home with the Star Trek Comics Megabundle! Since 1966, &lt;em&gt;Star Trek&lt;/em&gt; has inspired generations with bold, scifi-defining stories told across TV, film, games—and comics. Now, explore nearly 100 titles in this epic library, including &lt;em&gt;Star Trek: Strange New Worlds—The Illyrian Enigma&lt;/em&gt;, &lt;em&gt;Star Trek: Defiant, Vol. 1&lt;/em&gt;, &lt;em&gt;Star Trek, Vol. 1: Godshock&lt;/em&gt;, and many more. Pay what you want for stellar comics and help support The Comic Book Legal Defense Fund with your purchase!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#0"&gt;Pay $4 to unlock!&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#startrek_vol1"&gt;Star Trek, Vol. 1&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#boldlygo_vol1"&gt;Star Trek: Boldly Go, Vol. 1&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#startrekclassicsvolume1_thegorncrisis"&gt;Star Trek Classics Volume 1: The Gorn Crisis&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#startrek_newvisions_vol1"&gt;Star Trek: New Visions, Vol. 1&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#bt12"&gt;Pay $12 or more to also unlock!&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#startrek_vol2"&gt;Star Trek, Vol. 2&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#startrek_vol3"&gt;Star Trek, Vol. 3&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#startrek_vol4"&gt;Star Trek, Vol. 4&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#startrek_vol5"&gt;Star Trek, Vol. 5&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#startrek_vol6_after