ls that shake the ground.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; 24 Gruffler Sounds – Grunts and guttural vocalizations from grotesque, heavy-set creatures.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; 28 Inhaler Sounds – Choking gasps, wheezing attacks, and breath-driven pain cues.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; 20 Misc Sounds – Clickers, garglers, rattlers, and unplaceable horrors.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; 23 Squealer Sounds – High-pitched, frantic cries from nightmare-fueled entities.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; 24 Wheezer Sounds – Labored exhales and panicked gasps with grim urgency.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; 30 Worbler Sounds – Distorted attacks, squelching deaths, and pained howls from malformed abominations.&lt;p&gt;Every sound in this pack is brand new and exclusive to Volume 2 – no recycled material. Each monster was carefully designed with layers of texture to add realism and weight to your mutants, aliens, and otherworldly threats.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;44.1kHz / 16bit&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Each file is tagged with detailed metadata for fast implementation.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h3 id="foley_handgunssoundfxpack"&gt;&lt;a id="foley_handgunssoundfxpack" href="https://youtu.be/rsYk6pKAQoU"&gt;Foley: Handguns Sound FX Pack&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/db49c7e354031e496eab0f6cf3bd0e15396f0565.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=63ba54a7f3fe415c4256116e24bfd9ad"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Introducing the Foley: Handgun Sound FX Pack by Ovani Sound – a comprehensive collection of detailed, high-fidelity handgun handling foley with no gunfire sounds, ideal for realistic weapon systems and immersive first-person experiences.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;With 361 total sounds, this pack includes everything from magazine handling and holstering to hammer clicks, dry triggers, and weapon pickups.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;• 76 9mm Pistol Sounds: Assembly, cocking, handling, dry trigger pulls, magazine inserts, table movement, and more.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt; 55 Ammo and Brass Sounds: Bullet casing drops, box handling, and various ammo types including 9mm, .45 ACP, and .38 Special.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; 99 Colt 1911 Pistol Sounds: Safety toggles, hammer movements, mag drops, table handling, rack slides, and loading sequences.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; 62 Holstering Sounds: Draw and insert movements for leather, kydex, and zippered holsters across three weapon types.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; 69 S&amp;amp;W Revolver Sounds: Cylinder actions, hammer cocks, trigger movements, reloading rounds, and detailed pickup/putdown foley.&lt;p&gt;Perfect for FPS games, military simulators, cinematic cutscenes, or any project where precise weapon handling is a must.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;44.1kHz / 16bit&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Each file is embedded with detailed metadata for rapid integration into your audio workflow.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h3 id="weaponry_melee"&gt;&lt;a id="weaponry_melee" href="https://youtu.be/ge7F-Z3s2S4"&gt;Weaponry: Melee&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/1081f701300ecd71bbc6ee188b50c0e6f9b9ac44.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=232961630d1eb74a0ff66039e19cd5ee"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Introducing the Weaponry: Melee Sound FX Pack by Ovani Sound – a brutal and detailed arsenal of handcrafted audio for melee-based combat systems. Whether you're building a medieval brawler, post-apocalyptic survival game, or fantasy RPG, these sounds deliver the weight, grit, and satisfaction of up-close battle.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;With 171 total sounds across blades, blunts, and polearms, this pack gives developers clean separation between weapon types and motion, supporting modular systems and animation layering.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;• 77 Blade Sounds: Large, medium, small, and thin strikes, parries, blocks, sheathing, and unsheathing – perfect for swords, daggers, or rapiers.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt; 41 Blunt Sounds: Hard-hitting impacts and handling sounds for maces, hammers, and clubs of all sizes.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; 53 Polearm Sounds: Wooden haft-based swipes, pierces, and defensive maneuvers for spears, halberds, and staff weapons.&lt;p&gt;Designed with action-RPGs and fighting systems in mind, each sound is clear, cinematic, and ready for implementation.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;44.1kHz / 16bit &lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;Each file is tagged with detailed metadata for fast implementation.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="weaponry_ranged"&gt;&lt;a id="weaponry_ranged" href="https://youtu.be/GPUNZ6-48WU"&gt;Weaponry: Ranged&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/d028310ba52c58935a705c028b94f091dfb0a874.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=bf851b3aa7c9695da217382ab80f7ee9"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Introducing the Weaponry: Ranged Sound FX Pack by Ovani Sound – an expertly curated library of projectile weapon sounds for stylized or historical combat systems. With rich, textured recordings that span gunpowder, bows, crossbows, and hand-thrown weapons, this pack gives your ranged attacks the bite they deserve.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Featuring 179 total sounds, you'll find immersive firing, reloading, and impact layers across a diverse arsenal, tailored for modular use in any shooter, RPG, or tactical game.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;• 62 Firearm Sounds: Arquebuses, muskets, flintlock pistols, and cannons – with matching shots, reloads, and impacts that bring historical weapons to life.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt; 84 Projectile Weapon Sounds: Includes longbows, crossbows, ballistae, slings, and small bows with layered draw, shot, and reload actions.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; 33 Throwable Weapon Sounds: Arrows, spears, knives, shurikens, and stones with satisfying throw-and-impact sequences.&lt;p&gt;Ideal for games set in medieval, pirate, steampunk, or fantasy worlds, these sounds pair well with both stylized and realistic visuals.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;44.1kHz / 16bit &lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;Each file includes detailed metadata for fast and accurate implementation.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="ntlanhlakutuvoiceoverpack"&gt;&lt;a id="ntlanhlakutuvoiceoverpack" href="https://youtu.be/efFavTnWU2o"&gt;Ntlanhla Kutu Voice Over Pack&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/8c936fb6fdbb1eebf6bf7bd364dc7546a59f6123.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=662e901e8640aa35b64eef6d0f57ac79"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0777/1491/5643/files/Ntlanhla_Kutu_Voice_Over_Pack.pdf"&gt;Click here to view the full list of voice lines in the Ntlanhla Kutu Voice Over Pack&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Fully voice any character with the Ntlanhla Kutu Voice Over Pack by Ovani Sound. Featuring over 600 professionally recorded voice lines, this pack provides a versatile range of tones and expressions, perfect for giving life to an otherwise silent character! No AI used, 100% Human voice recordings.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Categories Included:&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Accepting, Confirming, &amp;amp; Thanks – Kind, neutral, and rude variations for affirmation and gratitude.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Battle &amp;amp; Support Yells – Intense callouts and combat shouts for action-packed scenes.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Commands – Tactical and situational instructions in far and near variations.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Declining &amp;amp; Confrontational – Polite refusals to strong dismissals for complex interactions.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;General Comments – Relatable phrases like “Gross” and “What now” to add personality.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Greetings &amp;amp; Farewells – Friendly and dismissive greetings and goodbyes.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Puzzling – Lines for exploration and problem-solving scenarios.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Wordless Expressions – A large collection of attack grunts, laughs, gasps, sighs, and more.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;This pack offers everything you need to create authentic, engaging characters that resonate with players.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;44.1kHz/16bit&lt;/p&